## Seconds since epoch
query T
SELECT format_string('Epoch seconds: %ts', TIMESTAMP '1970-01-01 00:00:01');
----
Epoch seconds: 1

## Milliseconds since epoch
query T
SELECT format_string('Epoch millis: %tQ', TIMESTAMP '1970-01-01 00:00:01');
----
Epoch millis: 1000

## Full month name
